QuestData.Title: Warsong Scout Update
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Return to Warsong Scout in Ashenvale.
QuestData.CompletionText: Keep an eye out, $R. The elves are often hiding in the shadows...$B$BWe must always be watching. We have worked very hard to claim this land, and the elves are looking for a chance to take it from us.$B$BI assume you have my next orders from Kadrak?
QuestData.RewardText: Let Kadrak know of the success we have had here holding off the night elves. Our plans are going well.
